Basic For Loop:
<{ for( $i = 0; $i < 5; $i++ ) }>
    <p>Iteration <{ $i }></p>
<{ endfor }>

Countdown Loop:
<{ for( $j = 3; $j > 0; $j-- ) }>
    <p>Countdown: <{ $j }></p>
<{ endfor }>

Step by 2:
<{ for( $k = 0; $k < 10; $k += 2 ) }>
    <p>Even number: <{ $k }></p>
<{ endfor }>

Variable Limits:
<{ for( $n = $start; $n <= $end; $n++ ) }>
    <p>Number: <{ $n }></p>
<{ endfor }>

Nested For Loops:
<{ for( $x = 1; $x <= 2; $x++ ) }>
    <div>Outer: <{ $x }>
        <{ for( $y = 1; $y <= 2; $y++ ) }>
            <span>Inner: <{ $y }></span>
        <{ endfor }>
    </div>
<{ endfor }>